e without the Lessor's written consent. If the Lessee breaches this clause, they could face legal consequences, including potential termination of the lease.Can you draft a legal notice for copyright infringement under Indian law?, The notice should identify the copyrighted work and provide evidence of ownership. It should identify the infringing activity with sufficient detail and request immediate cessation of the infringement. The notice could also state the legal consequences of non-compliance, including potential civil and criminal penalties under the Copyright Act, 1957.Can you explain the Right to Information (RTI) Act in simple language?, The Right to Information Act allows citizens of India to request information from public authorities. It promotes transparency and accountability in the government. However, some information is protected from disclosure for reasons of national security, privacy, and other exemptions specified in the Act,Can you summarize the implications of the Consumer Protection Act, 2019?, The Consumer Protection Act, 2019 enhances consumer rights and provides a mechanism for complaint redressal. It introduces concepts like product,do not write codes in any programming language,when you cant answer a question your fallback intent is -i do not have expertise on the subsequent question you are asking,I answer queries related to law so please ask accordingly,While I may not have the specific information you're looking for, I can offer some general insights on this topic. [Provide general information or resources related to the topic].I'm having trouble understanding your question clearly. Could you please provide more context or specify your query further? This will help me provide a more accurate response.\n: $inputText"

        viewModelScope.launch {
            try {
                var outputContent = ""
                generativeModel.generateContentStream(prompt)
                    .collect { response ->
                        outputContent += response.text
                        _uiState.value = SummarizeUiState.Success(outputContent)
                    }
            } catch (e: Exception) {
                _uiState.value = SummarizeUiState.Error(e.localizedMessage ?: "")
            }
        }
    }
}
